descriptionHtml:
Create your Todo List, add your tasks into it be much more productive!

Fanya is a todo list application that manages your tasks with the most beautiful and simple interface.
You can organize your tasks on your home screen using our widget, or our calendar.
It's super easy to create tasks, view them in a daily base screen, add reminders with notifications.

The features of Fanya:
- Create & Update tasks with a beautiful and simple interface
- Add reminders with notifications for your tasks
- Manage your todo list from a home screen widget that looks fantastic.

- Create custom categories with custom colors to tag your tasks.
- Search your tasks
- Backup & Restore your full content between devices
- Import your Calendar events from Google and Microsoft Outlook calendar
- Dark Theme
- Full customer support

With this features it's easy to manage your tasks and todo list, organize your work and be much more productive then ever.

title: Fanya:To do list Tasks & Notes

creator: Fanya Todo list & Tasks Apps
descriptionHtml:
Fanya Is a To Do List, Calendar, Planner, Tasks, Memos & Reminders App With The Best Looking & Easy To Use Interface.

Fanya is a free to-do list, planner & calendar app for managing and organizing your daily tasks, to-do lists, notes, reminders, checklists, calendar events, grocery or shopping lists, you can even manage student projects.


📅 Organize Your Tasks & To-Do Lists

• PLANNER & CALENDAR - Keep your to-do list and calendar events always at hand with our calendar widget. Fanya to-do list & planner support daily calendar view, Ongoing calendar view & agenda view, with built-in reminders.

• SET REMINDERS - One time reminders, recurring reminders to get your job done.


ASK MANAGEMENT
Add a to do list item straight from your Home screen or using Fanya, seperate your tasks into categories and manage them with more productivity.


For better task management flow we added a calendar integration to keep your agenda always up to date, in addition, we offer a free integrations with with Google Calendar, Outlook, Gmail, Google Tasks and Microsoft to-do.
For better productivity, we added recurring reminders, location reminders, one-time reminder and notes.
To keep your to do list up to date, we’ve added a daily planner and a focus feature that checks your productivity based on your tasks completion and entertainment apps usage.


DAILY PLANNER
Fanya is a to do list, a calendar, an inbox, a notepad, a checklist, task list, a board for post its or sticky notes, a task & project management tool, a reminder app, a daily planner, a family organizer, an agenda, a bill planner and overall the best productivity tool you will ever have.


GROCERY LIST & SHOPPING LIST
Fanya task list, calendar, agenda, reminders & planner is also great for shopping lists at the grocery store. Simply create a list on Fanya.
